    public class PlatformFlowManager
extends FlowManagerBase
implements ReplayStrategyRegistry
    A Camel-specific FlowManager implementation. Instances of this class are Autowired with a ReplayStrategy instance if managed within a Spring application context.

    Martin Krasser
